> Sports Dobbs helps Vols rally for 38-31 victory over No. 19 Georgia Tennessee running back Alvin Kamara (6) runs for a yardage as he's hit by Georgia linebacker Tim Kimbrough (42) during the first half of an NCAA college football game Saturday, Oct. 10, 2015, in Knoxville, Tenn.
